Dolly Parton announces 30-track Rock album ‘Rockstar’ out November 17th.
It includes collaborations with Lizzo, Miley Cyrus, Paul McCartney, Ringo Starr, Mick Fleetwood, Steve Perry, Kid Rock, Chris Stapleton, Pink, Brandi Carlile, Elton John, Stevie Nicks and more.
